[
  {
    "//": "How this artifact functions: The censer is perfectly mundane, The different types of incenses it can burn effectively function as different active abilities, but they all need high resonance to trigger. Purple incense grants enough resonance to use the rest of incenses, as well as enabling other highland artifacts.",
